node.text:
In this episode of The Wolf’s Den, JB meets Jason Oppenheim, a real estate agent, from Netflix’s Selling Sunset. While Netflix may have helped him become a household name, Jason and the Oppenheim Group have been synonymous with high quality service for years. He’s afforded his dream life by selling other’s their dream homes. And he’s here to tell you exactly how he closed the deal on his successful life. You’re not gonna wanna miss this!
